section.section.faq
  .site-container.faq__container
    h2.faq__heading.second-heading.js-animated-heading
      | <span>Ответы</span> на частые вопросы
    .faq__content.grid-container
      .grid-container__block
        span.faq__small-legend Полезная информация
      .grid-container__block.faq__item-container
        ul.faq__list
          for item in faq_arr
            li.faq__item
              button.faq__btn.button-reset.js-drop-menu-btn
                span.faq__btn-txt= item
                span.faq__btn-icon
                  span
                  span
              .drop-menu-container.js-drop-menu-container
                .faq__item-body.drop-menu.js-drop-menu
                  p
